Name: HK\_N\_REP\_DEF
Desc: Number of Report Definitions in the Report Definition List (maximum number of housekeeping/diagnostic reports)

Name: HK\_MAX\_SID
Desc: Maximum value of a service 3 Structure Identifier (SID)

Name: HK\_COLLECT\_PER
Desc: Minimum collection period for service 3 reports

Name: HK\_MAX\_N\_SIMPLE
Desc: Maximum number of simply-commutated parameters in a housekeeping/diagnostic report

Name: HK\_MAX\_N\_GR
Desc: Maximum number of super-commutated groups in a housekeeping/diagnostic report

Name: HK\_MAX\_REP
Desc: Maximum value of the repetition number of a super-commutated group in a housekeeping/diagnostic report

Name: HK\_MAX\_N\_REP
Desc: Maximum number of data items in a super-commutated groups in a housekeeping/diagnostic report

Name: HK\_MAX\_ID
Desc: Maximum value of a data pool item identifier

Name: EVT\_EID1
Desc: Array of EVT\_N\_EID1 elements holding the level 1 event identifiers in ascending order

Name: EVT\_EID2
Desc: Array of EVT\_N\_EID2 elements holding the level 2 event identifiers in ascending order

Name: EVT\_EID3
Desc: Array of EVT\_N\_EID3 elements holding the level 3 event identifiers in ascending order

Name: EVT\_EID4
Desc: Array of EVT\_N\_EID4 elements holding the level 4 event identifiers in ascending order
